ca.polymtl.inf3995.oronos.services

Class OronosXmlParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.polymtl.inf3995.oronos.services.OronosXmlParser

  • public class OronosXmlParser
extends java.lang.Object

    Oronos Xml Parser

    This parser is specifically targeting Oronos rocket xml files. Each tag in the application will be created only if it exists in the xml, and according to the specifications of the xml.
    Since:
    2018-04-12
    Version:
    0.0
